Guillaume Emmanuel `` Guy-Manuel '' de Homem-Christo -LRB- -LSB- ɡi manɥɛl də ɔmɛm kʁisto -RSB- ; born 8 February 1974 -RRB- is a French musician , record producer , singer , songwriter , DJ and film director , best known for being one half of the French house music duo Daft Punk , along with Thomas Bangalter .
He has also produced several works from his record label Crydamoure with label co-owner Éric Chedeville .
He and Chedeville formed the musical duo Le Knight Club .